  "detailed_description": "Snowman Arena creates a space for closeness, shared moments and fun you'll happily remember. And tons of explosions of course.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>local multiplayer for up to 4 players<br></li><li>on-line game with friends using Steam Remote Play<br></li><li>World Leaderboard in singleplayer highscore mode<br></li><li>up to 3 players on one keyboard<br></li><li>gamepads support<br></li><li>bots<br></li><li>adjustable difficulty for each player to balance gameplay so everyone can enjoy the game<br></li><li>two movement styles<br></li><li>8 maps<br></li><li>5 projectiles and 5 power-ups</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768980/extras/82b0f6c23dbba85b7b439cb28bda6327.avif?t=1701783264\" width=600 height=70 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Modes</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Deathmatch<br></li><li>Team Deathmatch<br></li><li>Last Man Standing<br></li><li>Highscore</li></ul>",
